for the leaves i added a thing using functionalinterface of realistic movement of wind (using transition ofc).
Its realistic because its using sin(the function) consumer which is a wave function and the wind is also wave
and can be represented as such. the tree class is holding arrays of the leaves and of the log blocks.
and an arraylist of fruits , 
the reason its an arraylist because we dont know exactly how many fruits will be ...
the fruit suppose to give player health by using callbacks ...
